dagens: gives you todays dinner in sio cafeteria. Default one is ifi, but you can get a list of cafeterias using list as an argument
dag: prints the day and date. example: Thursday 2016/09/15
tbane: shows the next departures at stop(default is Forskningsparken)
trikk: shows the next departures at stop(default is Forskningsparken)
buss: shows the next departures for stop
vouchers: shows how many vouchers a user got. default is yourself
commit: gives you a random string to add to a commit message
wiki: Returns the link to the wiki
